data.description: Move in ready, spacious home on corner lot in a great neighborhood awaits your family. This home has large rooms with an abundance of space and storage including a partially finished basement with bonus room, home office and workshop. Your entertainment space continues to the fenced in yard with deck and patio. Master suite includes jetted tub and enormous walk-in closet with built-in organizers. Just a few of the recent updates include kitchen, roof, gutters with guards and 2nd HVAC unit for upper level. Don't miss your opportunity to make this house your home.  This is a must see property as pictures do not convey the space.
